### Describe the bug

When Binding Configuration Section with a Collection to a Record type with Primary Constructor, containing Collection, the collection values are duplicated.
Issue does not seem to appear with normal constructors in records.

### Expected Behavior

Binding collection with 2 values to a Record should result in a record holding 2 values in it's collection.

### Steps To Reproduce

## .csproj File

```csharp
<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>
    <ImplicitUsings>enable</ImplicitUsings>
    <Nullable>enable</Nullable>

    <IsPackable>false</IsPackable>
    <IsTestProject>true</IsTestProject>
